reviews.review_text: Incomplete but ok Thanx Jack and Rob.  A decent aud recording for the period.  Each set is incomplete and all songs have cuts.  Combined with what I had before I am getting close to a complete show.  There is a good deal of crowd chatter too.  A great Attics!  Peace
